<div class="ability explanation">
	<div class="title">Abilities</div>
	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/fd589517c61c65312e1509e13a36cd412.png"></span><span>Crimson Oath</span></dt><dd><div>Increases damage to scorchrent enemies<br>by 15% and force strike damage by 50%.<br><br>Using Road to Glory grants the user the<br>"Crimson Glory" effect and a strength amp<br>with a maximum team amp level of two.<br>After this amp is granted, this ability<br>will not grant it again for 30 seconds.<br><br>When Crimson Glory is active, the user's<br>next force strike will deal additional damage<br>and inflict scorchrend.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/9f9540aa3b892c485f82bfd1ef78b1b72.png"></span><span>Potent Stun Res +100%</span></dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to stun by 100%.<br>When the user is hit by an attack that would have<br>stunned them, their strength is increased by 15%<br>for 10 seconds. After activating, this buff will not<br>activate again for 15 seconds.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/b2f1d14494e80343f38734ca9a2b72842.png"></span><span>Striking Haste +15%</span></dt><dd><div>Increases skill gauge fill rate by 15%<br>when the user's force strikes connect.</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. The stats shown here represent the adventurer at level 100 with 70 mana nodes unbound.</div><div>2. The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities.</div><div>3. The stats for the adventurer included in this notification shown in any prior notifications or preview videos were the stats at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unbound.</div><div>4. When an adventurer&#39;s skill level increases, the skill gauge will fill more slowly when set as a shared skill.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1629093600,update_time1628743763